<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HoldOff — Know Why It Happens</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
      color: #e0e0e0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    header {
      padding: 20px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
      background: rgba(10, 5, 25, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #f472b6 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #b0b0b0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    .btn-signin {
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1);
      color: #a78bfa;
      border: 1px solid #a78bfa;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-signin:hover {
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 120px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 52px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #f472b6 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .subheading {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #c0c0c0;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .cta-section {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #f472b6 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      border: none;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.05);
      color: #e0e0e0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.2);
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.4);
      background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
    }

    .insight-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .insight-card {
      background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .insight-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.05);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .insight-card h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #a78bfa;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .insight-card p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b0b0b0;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 100px 0 50px 0;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .section-title .highlight {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #f472b6 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 0 40px;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .feature {
      border-left: 3px solid #a78bfa;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }

    .feature h4 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #b0b0b0;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .testimonial-section {
      background: rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.03);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
      padding: 80px 40px;
      margin: 80px 0;
    }

    .testimonial {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonial p {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .testimonial-author {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #a78bfa;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    footer {
      background: rgba(10, 5, 25, 0.8);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #808080;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .final-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 40px;
    }

    .final-cta h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .insight-cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HOLDOFF</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
      <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/signin" class="btn-signin">Sign In</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Know Why <span class="highlight">It Happens</span></h1>
    <p class="subheading">Why do people ghost? Why do they shut down? Why do you act the way you do? HoldOff shows you the real reasons.</p>
    <div class="cta-section">
      <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Start Understanding</a>
