    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h4>Pattern Detection</h4>
      <p>See the dynamics that repeat. Ghosting cycles. Avoidant patterns. Anxious attachments. The patterns that keep you stuck.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h4>Personal Insights</h4>
      <p>AI-powered analysis tailored to your conditions and history. Get feedback that's real, not generic.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h4>Pause Before You React</h4>
      <p>When you feel the urge to text, HoldOff gives you space. Space to think. Space to understand. Space to choose differently.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h4>Your Privacy, Protected</h4>
      <p>Your conversations stay yours. No judgment. No sharing. Just understanding and growth.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="final-cta">
    <h2>Stop playing games. Start understanding yourself.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #b0b0b0; margin-bottom: 30px;">Your mental health deserves care. Your relationships deserve clarity. You deserve answers.</p>
    <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Begin Your Journey</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
